<p><strong>Correcting/Updating/Deleting/Deactivating Personal Information</strong></p>
<p>If a user’s personal identity information (e.g., zip code, phone, email, or postal address) changes, or if a user no longer desires our service, we provide a way to correct, update, or delete/deactivate users’ personally identifiable information. Usually this is done on the Membership Application page or by emailing our <script type='text/javascript'>
