<p><strong>Notification of Changes</strong></p>
<p>If we change our privacy policy, we will post those changes to this privacy statement.</p>
<p><strong>Emailing the NAWCC</strong></p>
<p>The NAWCC mail server uses software that rejects emails with offensive wording or potentially fraudulent or threatening content. Legitimate email may be accidentally blocked from reaching its destination by this scanning software. If you have not received a reply to confirm receipt or think that your email may not have been delivered, please contact the intended recipient via phone.</p>
<p><strong>The Legal Stuff</strong></p>
<p><span id="{C89F9550-2737-488E-9E69-8FB6D398F488}">This online resource is provided as a service of the NAWCC. The NAWCC is not responsible for the opinions and information posted on this site by others. The NAWCC disclaims all warranties with regard to information posted on this site, whether posted by NAWCC or any third party; this disclaimer includes all implied warranties of merchantability and fitness. In no event shall NAWCC be liable for any special, indirect, or consequential damages or any damages whatsoever resulting from loss of use, data, or profits, arising out of or in connection with the use or performance of any information posted on this site.</span></p>
<p><span id="{78E5DB7E-4FFB-4147-BA30-A93A139C0A08}">Do not post any defamatory, abusive, profane, threatening, offensive, or illegal materials. Do not post any material protected by copyright without the permission of the copyright owner. By posting material, the posting party warrants and represents that he or she is the originator of the material, he or she owns the copyright with respect to the material, or he or she has received permission from the copyright owner to post the material. In addition, the posting party grants the NAWCC and users of this list the nonexclusive right and license to reference, quote, discuss, and cite the material, as well as third-party rights to display, copy, publish, distribute, transmit, print, and use portions of the material in accordance with U.S. and international copyright law according to the implied license under which it is shared here.</span></p>
<p><strong>Contact Information</strong></p>
<p>Users with questions or suggestions regarding our privacy policy should contact us at:</p>
